  "extras": {
    "summary": "AN ACT TO AUTHORIZE THE CITY OF PASS CHRISTIAN, MISSISSIPPI, THROUGH ITS MUNICIPAL LAW ENFORCEMENT, TO OPERATE AND USE ONE RADAR SPEED DETECTION DEVICE TO ENFORCE THE MOTOR VEHICLE SPEED LIMITS ON THOSE PORTIONS OF U.S. HIGHWAY 90 THAT ARE LOCATED WITHIN THE CORPORATE LIMITS OF THE CITY; AND FOR RELATED PURPOSES."
